metadata.name: Me
metadata.description:
It's sometimes amazing to me how one small person can have such big goals, desires, and dreams. 

It made me want to remember myself at this point. Just like that, at home, uncluttered, but with fire inside. 

With a great love for the world and a great desire to live, enjoy each day and pursue my dreams. 

I know for sure that all my goals will come true and I will have everything I once thought up in my head. 

Well, in the meantime, I'm 24 and I'm just starting my journey into nft. 
And I want to keep this meaningful moment for me ü§ç
